# Rich Layout Demo

> A terminal page can feel calm, structured, and beautiful without needing a DOM.
> Jaringan keeps the source plain while giving the browser richer render cues.

## Highlights

- aligned tables for compact comparisons
- quotes for editorial emphasis
- lists for skimmable structure
- rules for visual rhythm

---

| Element | Source shape | Browser feel |
| --- | --- | --- |
| Table | pipe rows | aligned columns |
| Quote | `>` lines | accent rail |
| List | `-` lines | cyan diamonds |
| Rule | `---` | subtle divider |

